<View height="100%" controllerName="UI5FioriForTools.controller.MainNavigation.Primary.Example3" 
	xmlns:core="sap.ui.core" 
	xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" 
	xmlns="sap.m">
	<Page class="sapUiContentPadding" title="List Report Floorplan (List)">
		<content>
			<List id="list" updateFinished="onUpdateFinished" items="{path:'/Employees'}">
				<headerToolbar>
					<Toolbar>
						<Title id="title" />
					</Toolbar>
				</headerToolbar>
				<items>
					<ObjectListItem title="{FirstName} {LastName}" type="Navigation" press="onPress">
						<attributes>
							<ObjectAttribute text="{EmployeeID}" />
							<ObjectAttribute text="{City}" />
							<ObjectAttribute text="{PostalCode}" />
							<ObjectAttribute text="{Country}" />
							<ObjectAttribute text="{HomePhone}" />
						</attributes>
					</ObjectListItem>
				</items>
			</List>
		</content>
	</Page>
</View>
